channel.title: Please help.. server logout
channel.description:
Alright, well the problem is; when I log into the server I automatically log out like instantly and it continues to log me out, the server is online and on port 43594 on which I have port forwarded. The error message I get is: Error:" T2 - 126,126,126 - 12,0,0 - 80,111,105,110,116,115,58,32,48,10,76,-59," That's from the Moparscape client. This is what the server command says. [Riotday] Connected - Game saved for player Riotday - [Riotday] Disconnected . I'm not sure of this problem and you're help would greatly be appreciated. I'm also using a 317 source, I've actually tried all types of sources. Nothing seems to work, so please help me..
Thanks, Riot
